com.ijunit.common.data
Class TestCondition

java.lang.Object
  com.ijunit.common.data.TestCondition

public class TestCondition
extends java.lang.Object

A POJO object for holding a test condition attributes. A Test condition represent a test case or a scenario for testing a functionality. It holds class name whosh functionality is being tested and test data which are used to test functionality.
